Revision history for Net::DNS::Multicast.


**** 0.10  Nov 25, 2023

	Code minimisation and general tidy up.


**** 0.09  Nov 22, 2023

	Precompile list of multicast socket options.


**** 0.08  Nov 20, 2023

	Enable $resolver->bgread to capture multiple responses.


**** 0.07  Nov 11, 2023

	Attempt to make code more portable.


**** 0.06  Nov 9, 2023

	Insert missing dependencies into distribution metadata.
	Restructure test scripts.


**** 0.05  Nov 6, 2023

	Refactor code to permit concurrent IPv6 and IPv4 m-DNS.


**** 0.04  May 13, 2023

	Rework cache_flush() to handle implicit RR class.


**** 0.03  May 11, 2023

	m-DNS flag tests require Net::DNS 1.38.


**** 0.02  May 10, 2023

	t/00-pod.t lists non-existent directory.

Feature rt.cpan.org #148274
	Support m-DNS unicast_response and cache_flush flags


**** 0.01  May 5, 2023

